# The Complete Example
Author: Test Writer
Draft: Second

## Dramatis Personae
### The Court
KING LEAR - King of Britain
CORDELIA - His youngest daughter

### The Earls
KENT - A loyal earl

## ACT I

### SCENE 1

> A dark heath. Thunder and lightning.

KING LEAR
Blow, winds, and crack your cheeks!
  Rage, blow!
  You cataracts and hurricanoes, spout!

> He tears at his robes.

// A moment of silence

CORDELIA
(gently)
Father, please come inside.

SONG 1 The Storm
KING LEAR
  The storm rages on,
  The wind howls and moans.
SONG END

===

### SCENE 2

KENT
My lord, I bring news.
